<div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
<h1 style="text-align:center;">Welcome to the Concentration Game</h1>
<h3 style="text-align:center;">Rules: all cards are face down with symbols on them.  There are two of each symbol, match cards two at a time until you've matched them all.  Enjoy!
</div>
